<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Rifat...</title>
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #000000; /* Pure Black Background */
            color: #ffffff; /* White Text */
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .message-container {
            max-width: 650px;
            text-align: left;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 3px solid #333333;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
            transition: opacity 1.5s ease, transform 1.5s ease;
        }

        p.visible {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .ending {
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            text-align: right;
            color: #aaaaaa;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="message-container">
        <p>Dekho Rifat, tumse bahut jyada pyar karta hun main. Itna ki batana mushkil hai.</p>
        
        <p>Par jo tumne mere saath kiya — woh bahut galat tha. Bahut zyada galat.</p>
        
        <p>Is tarah rulate ho mujhe, aur tumhe ehsas bhi nahi hota. Par ek din khuda ke saamne jawab dena padega tumhe. Har cheez ka hisaab hoga wahan.</p>
        
        <p>Agar tum Allah ko maanti hoti... toh aisa nahi karte mere saath kabhi.</p>
        
        <p>Ab main kya bataaun — jeene ka man hi nahi raha. Andar se toot gaya hun bilkul. Mann mein kitni cheezein aati hain... aisi cheezein jo sochni bhi nahi chahiye.</p>
        
        <p class="ending">Bas itna kehna hai — kash tumne samjha hota. Kash...</p>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Har line dheere-dheere screen par aayegi
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
            const paragraphs = document.querySelectorAll(".message-container p");
            
            paragraphs.forEach((p, index) => {
                setTimeout(() => {
                    p.classList.add("visible");
                }, index * 1200); // 1.2 seconds ka gap har line ke beech me
            });
        });
    </script>

</body>
</html>
